{
  "stem": "198.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 19.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Who didn't work did not get a ration.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You just had to work.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If you didn't work, you were dead.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You had absolutely nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there was-- the ghetto was very badly managed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They had no support.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They was-- the food was rotten before it was passed to the people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Whoever had somebody from the leaders, they got a little bit more.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But whoever didn't knew anybody, with no luck, got nothing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We just had to live for what we got.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were- we were given a home of people which already were sent away to extermination camps.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So everything was left.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And a little-- like in one room, maybe 10 people slept.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And every day, it was getting [? looser ?] and [? looser. ?] So we had more room and more room, because people died.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was terrible typhus going in ghetto on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It-- were terrible diseases, so people were dying.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I remember in ghetto, [SIGHS] going back when my mother died.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "This was 1942.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So many people were dying that they did not even have enough manpower to bury the people.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was-- it was typhus going.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "In fact, I was very lucky.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I have, once they tested me a while back.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I have typhus, but it's not active.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I was with so many sick people in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We made a lot of friendship in the court we lived.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I still have them up till now.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were young, and a few hours we could spend together after work.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we had very strong friendships.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We knew when it was the holiday.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we talked.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We sat around in the court.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we were just hoping for a better tomorrow.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We just was talking-- we just were talking, maybe this will end one day.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
